OL,3,C'Competitiveness' of airline pilot,
OL,4,C25, may have led to fatal balloon crash
OL,6,FA report by the Air Accidents
OL,7,FInvestigation Branch (AAIB) found the
OL,8,Fcrash happened when the balloon
OL,9,Fclimbed rapidly before its envelope `
OL,10,Fthe outer layer ` collapsed as a
OL,11,Fparachute inside it stalled.
OL,13,FInvestigators said the climb, the
OL,14,Fballoon's design and the weather
OL,15,Fconditions all likely contributed to
OL,16,Fthe crash.
OL,18,FThe accident happened while the
OL,19,Fballoon was climbing away from a
OL,20,Ftarget on which Mr Gregory had to drop
OL,21,Fa marker as part of the competition.
