OL,3,C'Competitiveness' of airline pilot,
OL,4,C25, may have led to fatal balloon crash
OL,6,FThe report stated he may have used a
OL,7,Fhigh rate of climb to "gain a
OL,8,Fcompetitive edge because of his desire
OL,9,Fto do well in the competition".
OL,11,FMr Gregory had competed in balloon
OL,12,Fcompetitions around the world for
OL,13,Fseveral years.
OL,15,FThe AAIB said it was told by several
OL,16,Fpeople who knew him that he was a
OL,17,F"very safe pilot" but was "competitive
OL,18,Fand wanted to win".
