OL,3,C'Competitiveness' of airline pilot,
OL,4,C25, may have led to fatal balloon crash
OL,6,FAn unnamed friend said he was one of
OL,7,F"the world's best pilots, but (he)
OL,8,Fwould push the limits of what (he)
OL,9,Fcould do".
OL,11,FInvestigators were also told the
OL,12,Fcompetition at which he died "held
OL,13,Fmore significance" as he had missed
OL,14,Fother events due to work commitments,
OL,15,Fand needed to achieve a high enough
OL,16,Fscore to qualify for international
OL,17,Fcontests.
OL,19,FThe balloon was a racing balloon built
OL,20,Fby Mr Gregory using "high quality
OL,21,Fmaterials", the AAIB said.
