OL,6,FThe report also noted there was "a
OL,7,Fstrong wind gradient on the day of the
OL,8,Faccident", and "climbing into a
OL,9,Fchanging wind can cause the balloon to
OL,10,Fdistort, increasing the chance of a
OL,11,Fstall".
OL,13,FMr Gregory's family has said he was a
OL,14,Fpassionate balloonist who "took one
OL,15,Flast flight, doing what he loved" when
OL,16,Fhe died.
