OL,3,C'Competitiveness' of airline pilot,
OL,4,C25, may have led to fatal balloon crash
OL,6,FIn a tribute, they said: "Peter
OL,7,FGregory. 25 years of living life to
OL,8,Fthe full."On the morning of Sunday
OL,9,F25th June, our Pilot Pete took one
OL,10,Flast flight, doing what he loved.
OL,12,F"Be it in a hot air balloon or as an
OL,13,FAirline Pilot, Peter's passion for
OL,14,Fflying was something his family and
OL,15,Ffriends could only admire and support
OL,16,Fhim towards."
OL,18,FHis family added: "When he set his
OL,19,Fheart to something, he'd never give
OL,20,Fup, he was driven and determined, and
OL,21,Fone could only watch on in awe.
